      "content": "The feeling that small actions are futile against vast crises is completely understandable, and no one can truly fix the entire planet alone. These feelings of hopelessness can become severe, but please hold on because your life has inherent value beyond the climate crisis. If you are having thoughts of ending your life, please reach out immediately to a crisis hotline; calling or texting 988 in the US and Canada connects you with trained support. There are people who want to help you through this overwhelming dread.",
      "source": "target",
